# Cursor rules (root)

Canonical policy lives in **`AGENTS.md`**. This file exists for editors that read `.cursorrules` at the repo root.

- Read **`AGENTS.md`** first, then **`project_status.md`**, then **`project_memory/index.json`** as described there.
- **Enforcement and layering:** `.cursor/rules/00-project-contract.mdc` (and other `.cursor/rules/*.mdc`).

Do not duplicate the full `AGENTS.md` body here — keep a single source of truth.
